'''''The Empire Strikes Back Weekly'' 118''' is the one hundred eighteenth issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[May 29]], [[1980]].

Starting with this issue, the series' title was changed from ''Star Wars Weekly'' as the adaptation of [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']] began. The numbering continued from the previous title, though this issue released on Thursday, unlike the prior and subsequent issues.

